message.content:
This session is being continued from a previous conversation that ran out of context. The summary below covers the earlier portion of the conversation.

Summary:
1. Primary Request and Intent:
   - Fix buggy salon selector drawer in avatar at `localhost:8080/salon/agenda` to match `localhost:3000/salon/agenda`
   - Add scroll to salon list in the drawer for many salons
   - Visual comparison of both agenda pages and align monorepo to prototype, including: fix desktop date format (remove year), add mobile active filter chips with individual removal
   - Control visibility of "Minha página web" and "Agendamento IA" buttons (went through multiple iterations: mobile-only dropdown → both sizes dropdown → standalone header buttons → icon-only orange buttons → repositioned next to select → select moved next to avatar)
   - Clone `https://github.com/designer976/v0-EasySalon.git` to verify reference header
   - Use the salon's actual web booking URL (via `slug`) for the "Minha página web" button

2. Key Technical Concepts:
   - **vaul Drawer**: `shouldScaleBackground`, direction-aware data attributes (`data-[vaul-drawer-direction=bottom]`), `max-h-[80vh]`, overlay animations
   - **React architecture**: lifting filter state, callbacks for child→parent communication, `useMemo` for derived state
   - **Tailwind CSS**: `md:hidden`, `hidden md:flex`, responsive breakpoints, `overflow-y-auto flex-1 min-h-0` for scroll
   - **TypeScript**: exported types (`FilterRemoveSignal`, `ProfessionalChip`), strict typing with generics
   - **Filter chip system**: `FilterRemoveSignal` with `version` counter pattern to trigger `useEffect`, individual filter removal signals
   - **Header layout**: `justify-between` flex layout with left (logo + buttons) and right (select + avatar) groups

3. Files and Code Sections:

   - **`frontend/src/components/ui/drawer.tsx`**
     - Root cause of drawer bug: `shouldScaleBackground = true` scaled the background when drawer opened
     - Replaced with prototype's newer vaul implementation
     ```tsx
     function Drawer({ ...props }: React.ComponentProps<typeof DrawerPrimitive.Root>) {
       return <DrawerPrimitive.Root data-slot="drawer" {...props} />
     }
     // DrawerContent now uses direction-aware classes:
     "data-[vaul-drawer-direction=bottom]:inset-x-0 data-[vaul-drawer-direction=bottom]:bottom-0 data-[vaul-drawer-direction=bottom]:mt-24 data-[vaul-drawer-direction=bottom]:max-h-[80vh] data-[vaul-drawer-direction=bottom]:rounded-t-lg data-[vaul-drawer-direction=bottom]:border-t"
     // Overlay: bg-black/50 with fade animations instead of bg-black/80
     // Handle bar: only shows for bottom drawers via group-data-[vaul-drawer-direction=bottom]
     ```

   - **`frontend/src/components/layout/Header.tsx`**
     - Drawer scroll: added `overflow-y-auto flex-1 min-h-0` to salon list div
     - "Minha página web" + "Agendamento IA": final state = icon-only standalone desktop buttons (orange) positioned before salon selector; also in dropdown for all screen sizes (no `md:hidden`)
     - Current right-side order: `🌐 icon` → `🤖 icon` → Salon selector → Avatar
     ```tsx
     {/* Left side */}
     <div className="flex items-center gap-3">
       <button onClick={onMenuClick} className="... md:hidden">
         <Menu />
       </button>
       <img src={easySalonLogo} className="hidden md:block h-7 w-auto" />
     </div>

     {/* Right side controls */}
     <div className="flex items-center gap-2 md:gap-4">
       {/* Minha página web + Agendamento IA — desktop only */}
       {isSalonArea && (
         <>
           <button
             onClick={() => window.open("/agenda-online", "_blank")}
             aria-label="Minha página web"
             className="hidden md:flex w-9 h-9 items-center justify-center border border-[#dd4227] rounded-lg hover:bg-[#dd4227]/10 transition-colors"
           >
             <AppWindow className="w-4 h-4 text-[#dd4227]" />
           </button>
           <button
             onClick={() => window.open("https://wa.me/5541992938071", "_blank")}
             aria-label="Agendamento IA"
             className="hidden md:flex w-9 h-9 items-center justify-center border border-[#dd4227] rounded-lg hover:bg-[#dd4227]/10 transition-colors"
           >
             <Bot className="w-4 h-4 text-[#dd4227]" />
           </button>
         </>
       )}
       {/* Salon selector — desktop only */}
       <div className="relative hidden md:block" ref={salonDropdownRef}>...</div>
       {/* User dropdown */}
       <div className="relative" ref={userDropdownRef}>...</div>
     </div>
     ```
     - In user dropdown, both buttons show for all sizes (no `md:hidden`):
     ```tsx
     {isSalonArea && (
       <>
         <button onClick={() => { setUserDropdownOpen(false); window.open("/agenda-online", "_blank"); }}
           className="w-full flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-3 ...">
           <AppWindow className="w-4 h-4 text-muted-foreground" />
           <span>Minha página web</span>
         </button>
         <button onClick={() => { setUserDropdownOpen(false); window.open("https://wa.me/5541992938071", "_blank"); }}
           className="w-full flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-3 ...">
           <Bot className="w-4 h-4 text-muted-foreground" />
           <span>Agendamento IA</span>
         </button>
       </>
     )}
     ```

   - **`frontend/src/components/agenda/AgendaFilters.tsx`**
     - Exported new types and replaced `clearTrigger` with `removeSignal`:
     ```tsx
     export type FilterRemoveSignal = {
       version: number;
       type: 'specialty' | 'professional' | 'status' | 'all';
       id?: string;
     };
     export type ProfessionalChip = { id: string; label: string; };
     ```
     - New props added to `AgendaFiltersProps`:
     ```tsx
     onSpecialtyLabelChange?: (label: string | null) => void;
     onProfessionalChipsChange?: (chips: ProfessionalChip[] | null) => void;
     removeSignal?: FilterRemoveSignal;
     ```
     - `handleSpecialtySelect` now calls `onSpecialtyLabelChange`
     - `handleProfessionalToggle` now calls `onProfessionalChipsChange` with mapped `{id, label}[]`
     - `clearFilters` resets both label callbacks
     - `removeSignal` useEffect replaces `clearTrigger`:
     ```tsx
     useEffect(() => {
       if (!removeSignal) return;
       if (removeSignal.type === 'all') clearFilters();
       else if (removeSignal.type === 'specialty') handleSpecialtySelect("all");
       else if (removeSignal.type === 'professional' && removeSignal.id) handleProfessionalToggle(removeSignal.id);
       else if (removeSignal.type === 'status') { setSelectedStatus(null); onStatusFilter(null); }
       // eslint-disable-next-line react-hooks/exhaustive-deps
     }, [removeSignal?.version]);
     ```

   - **`frontend/src/pages/salon/AgendaV2Page.tsx`**
     - Added `IconX` to imports
     - Imported `FilterRemoveSignal`, `ProfessionalChip` from `AgendaFilters`
     - New state and derived values:
     ```tsx
     const [removeSignal, setRemoveSignal] = useState<FilterRemoveSignal | undefined>(undefined);
     const [specialtyLabel, setSpecialtyLabel] = useState<string | null>(null);
     const [professionalChips, setProfessionalChips] = useState<ProfessionalChip[]>([]);

     const activeFilterChips = useMemo(() => {
       type ChipType = 'specialty' | 'professional' | 'status';
       const chips: Array<{ id: string; label: string; type: ChipType }> = [];
       if (specialtyLabel) chips.push({ id: 'specialty', label: specialtyLabel, type: 'specialty' });
       professionalChips.forEach(p => chips.push({ id: p.id, label: p.label.split(' ')[0], type: 'professional' }));
       if (statusFilter) chips.push({ id: statusFilter, label: statusFilter, type: 'status' });
       return chips;
     }, [specialtyLabel, professionalChips, statusFilter]);

     const handleRemoveChip = (chip: { id: string; type: 'specialty' | 'professional' | 'status' }): void => {
       setRemoveSignal(prev => ({ version: (prev?.version ?? 0) + 1, type: chip.type, id: chip.id }));
       if (chip.type === 'specialty') { setServiceFilter(null); setSpecialtyLabel(null); }
       else if (chip.type === 'professional') setProfessionalFilter(prev => { const next = (prev ?? []).filter(id => id !== chip.id); return next.length > 0 ? next : null; });
       else if (chip.type === 'status') setStatusFilter(null);
     };

     const handleClearAllFilters = (): void => {
       setRemoveSignal(prev => ({ version: (prev?.version ?? 0) + 1, type: 'all' }));
       setProfessionalFilter(null); setServiceFilter(null); setStatusFilter(null);
       setSpecialtyLabel(null); setProfessionalChips([]);
     };
     ```
     - Fixed desktop date format (removed year): `format(selectedDate, "EEEE (d 'de' MMMM)", { locale: ptBR })`
     - Added mobile filter chips row:
     ```tsx
     {activeFilterChips.length > 0 && (
       <div className="md:hidden flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap mb-3">
         {activeFilterChips.map((chip) => (
           <span key={chip.id} className="flex items-center gap-1 px-2 py-1 bg-muted rounded-full text-xs text-foreground">
